  <ExtendedSection language="en">
    <Title><![CDATA[New features in OpenCms 13.0]]></Title>
    <Section>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links>
          <link name="link0" internal="true" type="A">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/template-variants/]]></target>
            <uuid>5edd2f01-d1cc-11ec-9238-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
        </links>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>OpenCms 13 introduces a series of techniques to build <a href="%(link0)">Template variants</a>:</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[Master Configuration Chaining]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>A new technique to chain Sitemap master configurations. With chaining, one can combine, reduce, extend, or vary formatter and function definitions in sitemap master configurations.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
      <Link>
        <Text/>
        <URI>
          <link internal="true" type="WEAK">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/template-variants/master-configuration-chaining/]]></target>
            <uuid>7646af18-d1cc-11ec-9238-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
        </URI>
      </Link>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[Site Plugins]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>A new technique to add individual CSS resources and JavaScript resources to sites built upon the same template. Site plugins are a more flexible replacement for the "headincludes" feature.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
      <Link>
        <Text/>
        <URI>
          <link internal="true" type="WEAK">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/template-variants/site-plugins/]]></target>
            <uuid>8d7ee5fd-d1cc-11ec-9238-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
        </URI>
      </Link>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[Element Setting Overrides]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>A new technique to vary the display of content elements for sites that share a template.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
      <Link>
        <Text/>
        <URI>
          <link internal="true" type="WEAK">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/template-variants/element-setting-overrides/]]></target>
            <uuid>81203dda-d1cc-11ec-9238-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
        </URI>
      </Link>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[Add Content Restrictions]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>A new technique to reduce the complexity of modular templates. With <em>Add content restrictions,</em> creation of new pages can be made uniform and easier.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
      <Link>
        <Text/>
        <URI>
          <link internal="true" type="WEAK">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/template-variants/add-content-restrictions/]]></target>
            <uuid>9b250241-d1cc-11ec-9238-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
        </URI>
      </Link>
    </Section>
  </ExtendedSection>
